1. Patient Profile
2. Clinical Goal
3. Treatment Settings

Add Treatment Duration selector:

8 weeks
12 weeks
16 weeks
20 weeks

Add Metabolic Status selector:

Normal
Insulin resistance
Prediabetes
Type 2 Diabetes

Add Tempo selector:

Conservative
Standard
Aggressive

