STEP 2 — STRATEGY SELECTION
==================================================

Convert protocol selection into strategy selection.

Display:

- Recommended Strategy
- Alternative Strategies

Each strategy card must show:

- Duration
- Tempo
- Monitoring intensity
- Confidence score
- Key clinical justification
- Key difference from primary recommendation

Allow only ONE strategy selection.

==================================================
STEP 3 — SAFETY & MONITORING
==================================================

Add a dedicated monitoring panel.

Display:

- baseline required labs
- missing labs
- contraindications
- relative cautions

Show why each missing clinical input matters.

If required labs are missing:

Display direct action button to return to the relevant input step.

