==================================================

The timeline must show:

- exact dates
- week numbers
- phase names
- medication events
- monitoring checkpoints
- milestone events

Use the resolved adaptive protocol, not fixed hardcoded phases.

The selected duration must change the timeline length.

Monitoring events must appear visually distinct from medication events.

